{"tid":463100,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"朱經緯 :揮棍動作看似快但好輕力","createTime":"2017-11-09T07:45:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-10T01:51:36.000Z","uid":39464,"like":3,"dislike":88,"uniUserReply":105,"replies":[{"pid":"574eaae0dbc544a26e99b346960349fa6e3adb29","tid":463100,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T07:45:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171109/large/1510213380_f2b0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171109%2Flarge%2F1510213380_f2b0.jpg&h=83436017&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【15:25】<br />\n朱經緯又指，他打的首兩個人都只是打兩人的背囊，並指第二個人「你哋睇到佢哋連反應都無」，指自己的目的只是「裝凶作勢，要俾壓力佢哋離開」。裁判官看罷片段後即指「第二個男子被打後整個人向後倒，踎在地上，不是嗎?」朱急急辯稱在他揮拳前，有警員用手和盾牌推該男子，之後該男子才中棍。朱並形容：「這兩個是好aggressive既non compliance」。<br />\n<br />\n朱又解釋，揮棍的目是「compel佢個compliance(逼使服從)」，用棍方式是「whipping（鞭打）」，「即棍頭打到佢少少，動作看似很快，但好輕力」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171109/57437325\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171109%2F57437325&d=9d9uzMU%2FhGmeLAZeyFS39EkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=50695195\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171109%2F57437325&h=a9e79b2f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171109/57437325</a>"},{"pid":"5dfad8b5cec2436da6e1e399bb275ea224cdf251","tid":463100,"uid":51215,"like":75,"dislike":1,"score":74,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T07:46:55.000Z","msg":"要計返momentum"},{"pid":"72777a22b72f19c225c1a1a18c03df794ff544bd","tid":463100,"uid":70183,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T07:59:01.000Z","msg":"有冇片重溫"},{"pid":"190ebccae078061f922adfb9f6cfa65346e77b2a","tid":463100,"uid":12021,"like":42,"dislike":1,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T08:00:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已